  "title": "Commis Chef",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong><br />Assist in daily kitchen operations (prep, cooking, plating)<br />Support senior chefs in preparing pizzas, pasta, and starters<br />Maintain cleanliness and organisation of kitchen stations<br />Follow food hygiene, safety, and sanitation standards<br />Ensure consistent food quality and presentation<br />Assist with stock preparation and basic inventory checks<br />Work closely with kitchen and front-of-house team<br />Perform other kitchen-related duties as assigned</p><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br />1–2 years of kitchen experience preferred (<strong>fresh graduates welcome</strong>)<br />Willing to learn and take guidance from senior chefs<br />Reliable, punctual, and team-oriented<br />Must work weekends and public holidays (shift-based)<br />Comfortable working in a small, fast-paced kitchen<br />Basic English communication required</p><p><strong>Staff Benefits</strong><br />Staff meals provided<br />Medical and insurance coverage<br />Staff discounts<br />Supportive working environment<br />Opportunity to learn woodfired cooking and grow with the team<br /><br /><br /><strong>Candidates with earliest availability will be given priority</strong><br />We regret to inform only suitable candidates will be contacted</p>",
